        <div class="col-md-12 mg-bt-80">
          <p class='description'>
            We grew out of Silicon Valley with one aim, to bring back morals and ethics to the
            finance industry. Our company built its foundation out of a frustration from watching
            asset managers acting selfishly and hurting their investors tremendously. Consequently,
            we consider it safe to say that we are one of the most, if not the most, ethical and
            principled-laden financial management firms out there. Our foundation is built upon
            ethics in which the investors’ best interests and our managers’ aims are aligned. We are
            extremely opposed to what we call “reckless aggressiveness”, in which a fund may post
            exorbitant returns one year and tout it as a major success and then fail to address the
            fact that their aggressiveness also led to losses during a larger number of years. While
            this has become the norm in the asset management industry, our fund values
            responsible investment and asset management. Rather than posting exorbitant returns,
            we aim to deliver consistent returns to our investors, ensuring long-term performance as
            opposed to possible investments in other overly aggressive funds. Our goal at
            BlackVault Investments is simple: beat the market while protecting investors’ assets. Our
            creed is investor interests trump all. This gives us the confidence to open our doors
            completely to investors to communicate with their respective portfolio managers about
            their asset’s performance at any given time.
