    <section id="investment" class="services">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="header-content">
            <h2>Investment Process</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12 mg-bt-80 athelas">
          <p>
              We live in an ever-evolving world where markets are dynamic and expanding. Our
            team emphasizes the concept of globalization and following business trends as it is
            fundamental in our value-growth based approach. Most asset managers focus on very
            specific and limited regions or sectors. We find this to be constrictive and amateur as
            they often ignore market dynamics while also missing key opportunities in unexplored
            fields. We, however, utilize our unique combination of sophisticated and proven arbitrage
            strategies to expose market inefficiencies and access strategic, diverse, and global
            opportunities.
          </p>
          <p>
              Our strategy combines value and growth sectors and regions, packaging them
            together in a risk-averse asset allocation to deliver consistent, long-term returns. We
            consider top and bottom fundamental analytics as well as technical analytics to select
            potential investments. Our process evaluates companies through two proven methods:
            comparable companies and DCF. We utilize these metrics in tandem to both select
            investments and determine entry and exit points. We not only analyze value
            opportunities, but also growth opportunities. This unique blend gives us an advantage
            over many other value or growth-driven managers as it allows us to remain more
            diversified and more risk-averse.
          </p>
          <p>
              The significance of employing this approach, particularly without the constraints of
            silos or arbitrary limitations, is that we uncover an uncommon pool of opportunities,
            which we believe has little overlap with other asset managers. We believe that our
            investors are specifically drawn to our differentiated approach and portfolios. Over time,
            this has given us the added advantage of a committed investor base that has allowed us
            to see events through to their resolution.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
